Voyager New Moves

Eerie Terrain

Type Category PP Power Accuracy Description
10 0 Invert effectiveness, null protection, and boost Ghost.

Details

-Blocks protection move use

-Boosts damage from confusion by 30%

-Boosts ghost-type damage by 30%

-Inverts type effectiveness

-An even number of instances of the Inverse Battle effect results in normal type advantages. For example, a grounded attacker that uses Negative Energy during Eerie Terrain will attack with non-inverted Electric type effectiveness.
